What is recursive function
A recursive function is a function that calls itself until it needs to stop.

Simple samajh:
Function khud ko call karta hai
Har call me problem chhoti hoti jati hai


function printNumber(n) {
  if (n > 5) {
    return; // stop
  }
console.log(n); // print number
  printNumber(n + 1); // call next number
}
printNumber(1);
